title: Ceiling fans included, Spacious 9' ceilings, Stylish private cabanas

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-Resort-style landscaping and water features surround the community', '-Kitchen islands with designer pendant lighting in select floorplans', '-Amazing views of Boca Raton, the Boca Raton Country Club and beaches from upper level residences', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-Chef-caliber kitchens featuring 48-inch cabinets', '-Powder rooms in select residences', '-Additional premium storage space available', '-Bike repair shop and interior bike storage', "-Spacious 9' ceilings", '-Wood flooring throughout the kitchen, living and dining areas', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
